ThinkPart(
    type='think',
    think='Now I can see several issues clearly:\n\n1. **API Path Double Prefixi
ng**: `main.ts` sets `app.setGlobalPrefix("api/v1")`, but `AuthController` uses 
`@Controller("api/v1/auth")`. This means the actual path would be `/api/v1/api/v
1/auth` - double prefixed! Meanwhile, `BlocksController` and `ReportsController`
use `"blocks"` and `"reports"` which would correctly map to `/api/v1/blocks` and
`/api/v1/reports`.\n\n2. **Missing Validation in RegisterDto**: `RegisterDto` ha
s no `@IsString()`, `@IsNotEmpty()`, or `@IsDateString()` decorators.\n\n3. **En
tities not centralized**: `BlockEntity` and `ReportEntity` are in their module f
olders but not exported from `database/entities/index.ts`. Since `autoLoadEntiti
es: true` is set in TypeOrmModule, this might work, but it\'s inconsistent with 
the project structure. Also, the NestJS design doc says entities should be in `d
atabase/` or module `entities/` subfolder, which they are... but the main `datab
ase/entities/index.ts` doesn\'t export them.\n\n4. **Missing `deleted_at` in Blo
ckEntity**: Per `docs/design-docs/db.md`: "每张表必须包含 `created_at` 和 `updat
ed_at`" and "软删除：使用 `deleted_at`（nullable datetime），不直接物理删除". `B
lockEntity` is missing `updated_at` and `deleted_at`! Wait, does db.md say ALL t
ables MUST have `deleted_at`? It says "软删除：使用 `deleted_at`（nullable datet
ime），不直接物理删除". This implies all tables should have it. BlockEntity only
has `created_at` and is missing `updated_at` and `deleted_at`.\n\n5. **Missing m
odules docs**: The PR added new modules (auth, blocks, reports, content-moderati
on, admin) but I need to check if docs/modules/INDEX.md was updated with these. 
Looking at the read of docs/modules/INDEX.md, it DOES list auth, matching, im, a
dmin, blocks-reports, content-moderation. But wait - blocks-reports is one doc w
hile the code has two separate modules. That\'s probably fine. But are the indiv
idual markdown files actually present?\n\nLet me check if the module docs actual
ly exist.',
    encrypted=None
)
